Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Energy assistance bill
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w4kl
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 31 Aug 1980
Surprise swing of Republican voting in favour of the cold north over energy assistance bill. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less